msgstr "معدل الخصم"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/present_value_calculator.html:189
msgid ""
"The discount rate reflects your required return or opportunity cost. Higher "
"rates result in lower present values, reflecting greater risk or better "
"alternatives."
msgstr ""
"يعكس معدل الخصم العائد المطلوب أو تكلفة الفرصة البديلة. ويؤدي ارتفاع "
