#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:284
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:338
msgid "What is Conception?"
msgstr "ما هو الحمل؟"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:286
msgid ""
"Conception occurs when a sperm fertilizes an egg, typically happening during"
" ovulation. This is the moment when pregnancy begins, and it usually occurs "
"about 14 days after the start of your last menstrual period (LMP) in a "
"28-day cycle."
msgstr ""
"يحدث الحمل عندما يقوم الحيوان المنوي بتخصيب البويضة، ويحدث ذلك عادةً أثناء "
"الإباضة. هذه هي اللحظة التي يبدأ فيها الحمل، وعادة ما يحدث بعد حوالي 14 "
"يومًا من بدء آخر دورة شهرية (LMP) في دورة مدتها 28 يومًا."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:289
msgid ""
"The conception date is important for tracking fetal development, "
"understanding pregnancy milestones, and calculating your due date. However, "
"it's important to note that the exact moment of conception is difficult to "
"determine precisely."
msgstr ""
"يعد تاريخ الحمل مهمًا لتتبع نمو الجنين وفهم مراحل الحمل وحساب موعد ولادتك. "
"ومع ذلك، من المهم ملاحظة أنه من الصعب تحديد لحظة الحمل بدقة."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:295
msgid "How Conception Date is Calculated"
msgstr "كيف يتم حساب تاريخ الحمل"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:300
msgid ""
"Conception typically occurs approximately 266 days (38 weeks) before the due"
" date. This is calculated by subtracting 266 days from your expected due "
"date."
msgstr ""
"يحدث الحمل عادةً قبل 266 يومًا تقريبًا (38 أسبوعًا) من الموعد المحدد. ويتم "
"حساب ذلك عن طريق طرح 266 يومًا من تاريخ ولادتك المتوقع."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:302
msgid "Formula: Conception Date = Due Date - 266 days"
msgstr "الصيغة: تاريخ الحمل = تاريخ الاستحقاق - 266 يومًا"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:305
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:77
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:81
msgid "From Last Menstrual Period"
msgstr "من الدورة الشهرية الأخيرة"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:307
msgid ""
"Conception typically occurs around 14 days before your next expected period."
" For a 28-day cycle, this is 14 days after the first day of your last "
"period."
msgstr ""
"يحدث الحمل عادةً قبل حوالي 14 يومًا من الدورة الشهرية المتوقعة التالية. "
"بالنسبة لدورة مدتها 28 يومًا، يكون ذلك بعد 14 يومًا من اليوم الأول من آخر "
"دورة شهرية لك."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:309
msgid "Formula: Conception Date = Last Period + (Cycle Length - 14 days)"
msgstr "المعادلة: تاريخ الحمل = آخر دورة شهرية + (مدة الدورة - 14 يومًا)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:318
msgid "Choose your calculation method: From Due Date or From Last Period"
msgstr "اختر طريقة الحساب الخاصة بك: من تاريخ الاستحقاق أو من الفترة الأخيرة"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:319
msgid "If using due date method, enter your expected due date"
msgstr "إذا كنت تستخدم طريقة تاريخ الاستحقاق، فأدخل تاريخ الاستحقاق المتوقع"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:320
msgid ""
"If using last period method, enter the first day of your last menstrual "
"period and your cycle length (default: 28 days)"
msgstr ""
"إذا كنت تستخدمين طريقة آخر دورة شهرية، فأدخلي اليوم الأول من آخر دورة شهرية "
"لك وطول دورتك (الافتراضي: 28 يومًا)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:321
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:341
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:373
msgid "Click 'Calculate' to see your results"
msgstr "انقر فوق \"احسب\" لرؤية نتائجك"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:322
msgid ""
"Review your conception date, pregnancy timeline, and trimester information"
msgstr "راجعي تاريخ الحمل والجدول الزمني للحمل ومعلومات الثلث"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:323
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:343
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:365
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your pregnancy progress"
msgstr "استخدمي الرسوم البيانية لتصور تقدم حملك"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:334
msgid ""
"The estimated date when conception likely occurred. This is typically within"
" a 5-6 day window around ovulation when the egg is viable for fertilization."
msgstr ""
"التاريخ المقدر لحدوث الحمل على الأرجح. يتم ذلك عادةً خلال فترة تتراوح من 5 "
"إلى 6 أيام حول الإباضة عندما تكون البويضة قابلة للتخصيب."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:338
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:364
msgid "Last Menstrual Period (LMP)"
msgstr "آخر دورة شهرية (LMP)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:340
msgid ""
"The first day of your last menstrual period. This is used as the starting "
"point for calculating pregnancy weeks and due date."
msgstr ""
"اليوم الأول من آخر دورة شهرية لك. ويستخدم هذا كنقطة بداية لحساب أسابيع الحمل"
" وتاريخ الولادة."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:346
msgid ""
"The estimated date when your baby is due. This is calculated as 280 days (40"
" weeks) from the first day of your last menstrual period."
msgstr ""
"التاريخ المقدر لولادة طفلك. يتم حساب ذلك على أنه 280 يومًا (40 أسبوعًا) من "
"اليوم الأول لآخر دورة شهرية لك."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:350
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:370
msgid "Weeks and Days Pregnant"
msgstr "أسابيع وأيام الحمل"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:352
msgid ""
"The number of weeks and days since your last menstrual period. Pregnancy is "
"typically counted from the LMP, not from conception."
msgstr ""
"عدد الأسابيع والأيام منذ آخر دورة شهرية لك. عادة ما يتم حساب الحمل من الدورة"
" الشهرية الأخيرة، وليس من الحمل."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:358
msgid ""
"Your current trimester: First (weeks 1-13), Second (weeks 14-27), or Third "
"(weeks 28-40). Each trimester has different developmental milestones."
msgstr ""
"الثلث الحالي من الحمل: الأول (الأسابيع 1-13)، الثاني (الأسابيع 14-27)، أو "
"الثالث (الأسابيع 28-40). كل ثلاثة أشهر لها معالم تنموية مختلفة."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:362
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:382
msgid "Progress Percentage"
msgstr "نسبة التقدم"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:364
msgid ""
"The percentage of your pregnancy completed based on a full 40-week (280-day)"
" pregnancy term."
msgstr ""
"النسبة المئوية لحملك المكتمل بناءً على فترة حمل كاملة مدتها 40 أسبوعًا (280 "
"يومًا)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:372
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:333
msgid "Pregnancy Trimesters"
msgstr "الثلث من الحمل"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:375
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:450
msgid "First Trimester (Weeks 1-13)"
msgstr "الأشهر الثلاثة الأولى (الأسابيع 1-13)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:377
msgid ""
"Early development, organ formation, and initial fetal growth. Many women "
"experience morning sickness and fatigue during this period."
msgstr ""
"التطور المبكر، وتكوين الأعضاء، والنمو الأولي للجنين. تعاني العديد من النساء "
"من غثيان الصباح والتعب خلال هذه الفترة."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:379
msgid ""
"Key milestones: Heartbeat begins, major organs form, baby's sex is "
"determined"
msgstr ""
"المعالم الرئيسية: يبدأ نبض القلب، وتتشكل الأعضاء الرئيسية، ويتم تحديد جنس "
"الطفل"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:382
msgid "Second Trimester (Weeks 14-27)"
msgstr "الفصل الثاني (الأسابيع 14-27)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:384
msgid ""
"Rapid growth, movement felt, and visible baby bump. Often called the "
"'honeymoon period' of pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"نمو سريع، وشعور بالحركة، ونتوء واضح للطفل. غالبا ما تسمى \"فترة شهر العسل\" "
"من الحمل."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:386
msgid ""
"Key milestones: Baby movements felt, anatomy scan, baby can hear sounds"
msgstr ""
"المعالم الرئيسية: الشعور بحركات الطفل، والمسح التشريحي، ويمكن للطفل سماع "
"الأصوات"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:389
msgid "Third Trimester (Weeks 28-40)"
msgstr "الفصل الثالث (الأسابيع 28-40)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:391
msgid ""
"Final growth phase, preparation for birth, and increased discomfort. Baby "
"gains most weight during this period."
msgstr ""
"مرحلة النمو النهائية، والتحضير للولادة، وزيادة الانزعاج. يكتسب الطفل أكبر "
"قدر من الوزن خلال هذه الفترة."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:393
msgid ""
"Key milestones: Baby reaches full term (37 weeks), lungs mature, ready for "
"birth"
msgstr ""
"المعالم الرئيسية: يصل الطفل إلى فترة الحمل الكاملة (37 أسبوعًا)، وتنضج "
"الرئتان، وتكونان جاهزتين للولادة"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:400
msgid "Understanding the Conception Window"
msgstr "فهم نافذة الحمل"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:402
msgid "Conception can occur within a 5-6 day window around ovulation:"
msgstr "يمكن أن يحدث الحمل خلال فترة 5-6 أيام حول الإباضة:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:405
msgid "Sperm can survive in the female reproductive tract for up to 5 days"
msgstr ""
"يمكن للحيوانات المنوية البقاء على قيد الحياة في الجهاز التناسلي الأنثوي لمدة"
" تصل إلى 5 أيام"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:406
msgid ""
"The egg is viable for fertilization for about 12-24 hours after ovulation"
msgstr "تبقى البويضة قابلة للتخصيب لمدة 12-24 ساعة بعد الإباضة"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:407
msgid ""
"The most fertile window is typically 2-3 days before ovulation and the day "
"of ovulation"
msgstr ""
"عادةً ما تكون الفترة الأكثر خصوبة هي 2-3 أيام قبل الإباضة ويوم الإباضة"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:408
msgid ""
"The calculator provides an estimated conception date, but actual conception "
"may have occurred within a few days of this date"
msgstr ""
"توفر الآلة الحاسبة تاريخًا تقديريًا للحمل، ولكن قد يكون الحمل الفعلي قد حدث "
"خلال أيام قليلة من هذا التاريخ"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:420
msgid ""
"Conception dates are estimates. The exact moment of conception is difficult "
"to determine, and actual conception may have occurred within a 5-6 day "
"window around the calculated date."
msgstr ""
"مواعيد الحمل هي تقديرات. من الصعب تحديد اللحظة الدقيقة للحمل، وربما حدث "
"الحمل الفعلي خلال فترة تتراوح من 5 إلى 6 أيام حول التاريخ المحسوب."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:426
msgid ""
"Pregnancy is typically counted from the first day of your last menstrual "
"period (LMP), not from conception. This is why pregnancy is said to last 40 "
"weeks even though conception occurs about 2 weeks after LMP."
msgstr ""
"عادة ما يتم حساب الحمل من اليوم الأول لآخر دورة شهرية (LMP)، وليس من لحظة "
"الحمل. ولهذا السبب يقال أن الحمل يستمر 40 أسبوعًا على الرغم من أن الحمل يحدث"
" بعد حوالي أسبوعين من آخر دورة شهرية."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Individual cycle lengths vary. If your cycle is longer or shorter than 28 "
"days, adjust the cycle length in the calculator for more accurate results."
msgstr ""
"تختلف أطوال الدورات الفردية. إذا كانت دورتك أطول أو أقصر من 28 يومًا، فاضبطي"
" طول الدورة في الآلة الحاسبة للحصول على نتائج أكثر دقة."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:438
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:464
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational and informational purposes only. Always "
"consult with healthcare providers for accurate pregnancy dating, especially "
"for medical decisions and prenatal care."
msgstr ""
"هذه الآلة الحاسبة للأغراض التعليمية والإعلامية فقط. استشيري دائمًا مقدمي "
"الرعاية الصحية للحصول على مواعيد دقيقة للحمل، خاصة فيما يتعلق بالقرارات "
"الطبية والرعاية السابقة للولادة."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:522
msgid "Please enter a due date."
msgstr "الرجاء إدخال تاريخ الاستحقاق."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:533
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:550
msgid "Please enter your last menstrual period date."
msgstr "الرجاء إدخال تاريخ آخر دورة شهرية لك."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:789
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:845
msgid "Completed"
msgstr "مكتمل"

