#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:355
msgid "Heat index is most accurate in shaded, light wind conditions."
msgstr "يكون مؤشر الحرارة أكثر دقة في ظروف الرياح المظللة والخفيفة."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/heat_index_calculator.html:356
